  "body": "Use a pattern of internal errors to attach common metadata in a bigger try / catch:\r\n\r\n```ts\r\ntry {\r\n  if (numBits !== 1) {\r\n    throw new AttestationError({\r\n      code: AttestationErrorCode.NOT_EXACTLY_ONE_AGGREGATION_BIT_SET,\r\n      numBits,\r\n    });\r\n  }\r\n} catch (e) {\r\n  throw new AttestationError(e.type, attestationJob);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nExample in code\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/4c43371276f18dc453256192f2ab8a2941653afd/packages/lodestar/src/network/reqresp/request/index.ts#L140-L142",
